post.description:
Clone a flow — deep copy with new IDs for flow, nodes, and edges.

Returns the new flow ID and name. The caller can use GET /flows/{new_id}
to retrieve the full cloned flow.

put.description:
Set the notification configuration for a workflow.

Body shape:
    {
        "on_complete": [{"type": "email"|"slack"|"webhook", ...}],
        "on_failure":  [{"type": "email"|"slack"|"webhook", ...}]
    }
